{"tid":1171633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【華為危機】傳向多間銀行尋求$78億離岸貸款 美國禁令後首次","createTime":"2019-05-25T23:54:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T05:41:09.000Z","uid":28114,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6badfeb4c00c515b5780510fc6343848e3a99909","tid":1171633,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T23:54:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190525/large/1558750529_6e0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190525%2Flarge%2F1558750529_6e0a.jpg&h=5c1f1a32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傳華為正尋求78億元離岸貸款。(路透社)<br />\n<br />\n彭博社引述知情人士報道，中國電訊設備商華為，正向多間銀行尋求約10億美元（約78億港元）的貸款，這是美國對華為實施限制、要求科技公司切斷與華為的關係後，華為首次尋求大規模的融資。華為至今日仍未對事件回應。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士指出，華為希望尋求美元或港元的離岸貸款，目標年期分是5年和7年。華為目前與銀行的磋商仍在初步階段，不一定保證能達成協議。不過，知情人士指出，若果華為能夠達成貸款協議，從貸款的定價、參與的銀行，可以反映目前市場對華為財務實力的看法。<br />\n<br />\n華為2018年的年報顯示，截至去年12月華為的無擔保銀行貸款總額為370億元人民幣（下同，約420億港元），其中28億元（約31.8億）貸款會在1年內到期。華為的現金和現金等價物的總額，約為貸款總額的2.6倍。<br />\n<br />\n華為在4個月前曾經向5間內地的銀行貨款，總額為140億元（約159億港元），而去年9月華為則向10間銀行，進行15億美元（約117億港元）離岸貸款。<br />\n<br />\n另外，Google宣佈終止與華為合作，手機不會獲Android更新，引發台灣三大主要電信商已宣佈停止引入華為手機。華為台灣的代理商訊崴技術，將在下周一與台灣5大電信商負責人會面，講述這次Google決定的影響。<br />\n<br />\n彭博社/台灣《工商時報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190525/59639396\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190525%2F59639396&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=fbbea036\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190525%2F59639396&h=28414359\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190525/59639396</a>"},{"pid":"56d443195d164fc73229406b366348c86df35e18","tid":1171633,"uid":41245,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T23:57:19.000Z","msg":"依個世界依家債仔大過債主㗎<br />\n又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8930a8a63f31b0616d9b71810ca33d84c3609fe5","tid":1171633,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T00:17:59.000Z","msg":"咁大個中國政府背景都要借10億美金？"},{"pid":"f42becfd38f850d9e386dd65a69d956665aa0f6e","tid":1171633,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8930a8a63f31b0616d9b71810ca33d84c3609fe5","tid":1171633,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T00:17:59.000Z","msg":"咁大個中國政府背景都要借10億美金？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T00:18:25.000Z","msg":"美金"},{"pid":"7364613aa9eae8d5ceb8c71614d16e44290964bb","tid":1171633,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T00:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba14376c02da90f0b29cf52f8cf94d35690b4e0","tid":1171633,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f42becfd38f850d9e386dd65a69d956665aa0f6e","tid":1171633,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8930a8a63f31b0616d9b71810ca33d84c3609fe5","tid":1171633,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T00:17:59.000Z","msg":"咁大個中國政府背景都要借10億美金？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T00:18:25.000Z","msg":"美金"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T00:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nD美金又要用黎買石油糧食、又要一帶一路幫非洲、又要救海航華為"},{"pid":"772e74fd072ee57abc52d740e1ef2a386ce361e3","tid":1171633,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T02:52:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa